HEADWORD: Monoecian
<hw>Mo*noe"cian</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Of or pertaining to the Monoecia;
monoecious.</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>One of the
